Stacey H
A well balanced bike tour of countryside Hoi An
Oct 2022 • Solo
Vu is very warm and personable. Throughout my bike trip, I got to ride a water buffalo, enjoy a basket boat (we caught 3 crab!), and learn the history of the villages we visited. I would recommend this trip to anyone that wants to see Hoi An in a different light outside of Old Town.
