Awesome tour of the Ba Na Hills!
Oct 2023 • Solo
Vu was a great guide! He is very knowledgeable about the history of Vietnam!
Our tour lasted about seven hours and we were able to see and learn about every aspect of Ba Na Hills! I would recommend Vu and his tour, he made sure we saw everything and we had free time at the end for games at the amusement park and lunch. Vu also knows the perfect spots to take great photos! If you want a thorough and enjoyable tour…book this one!

