Wonderful food, super guide and plenty of learning along the way!
Jul 2022 • Couples
We had an absolutely fantastic food tour in Hoi An led by our wonderful guide Vu. We enjoyed a wide range of traditional Vietnamese street food along our tour and we particularly enjoyed the information and history shared by Vu as we visited each stop on the tour. We found this very interesting and enjoyed learning a lot about Hoi An. We ate in delicious places that we definitely would not have found ourselves. Thank you very much Vu! I will certainly be recommending this tour to all of my friends that visit Hoi An in the future.
